entries.femaleVariant: Straight to the point. I like it.

entries.maleVariant: You recommend any chrome in particular?

entries.femaleVariant: Eh, y'know, cyberimplantation is like buying shoes – everyone needs somethin' different. A netrunner won't have the same needs as a solo.
But...! If you spend a lotta time in the Badlands, it's worth investing in cloaking gear. Holoskin, active camo – what have you.
Compared to the city, surrounding area might look deserted... but less folk doesn't mean you'll be safer.
Here's what I recommend – move quietly, don't draw too much attention, else things can get real ugly, real quick.
I know. I was raised by the Bakkers.
Oh, well I don't have to tell you, then.
